            </svg>
            GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </Card>

      <!-- Chzzk Karaoke Overlay -->
      <Card class="project-card">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-icon">🎤</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="project-title">Chzzk Karaoke Overlay</h3>
            <p class="project-role">OBS 스트리밍 오버레이</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <span class="project-date">2024 ~ Present</span>

        <p class="project-desc">
          치지직 스트리머를 위한 <strong>노래방 오버레이</strong>.
          React + Supabase 실시간 동기화, Vercel 배포.
        </p>

        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">React</span>
          <span class="tag">TypeScript</span>
          <span class="tag">Supabase</span>
          <span class="tag">Zustand</span>
        </div>

        <div class="project-links">
